'''Northlands''' was a vague term for the lands north of [[Beleriand]], including [[Ard-galen]]/[[Anfauglith]], the [[Iron Mountains|Ered Engrin]], and probably [[Hithlum]].<ref>{{HM|Guide}}, entry "Northlands"</ref>

After Beleriand sank beneath the [[Belegaer|Sea]], "Northlands" became used more broadly for the northern regions of [[Middle-earth]], such as [[Northern Waste|Forodwaith]].{{fact}}

